Date: Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:54:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] mm: enable amlogic vmap stack for arm64. [1/1]

PD#SWPL-188077

Problem:
optimizate kernel stack.

Solution:
enable amlogic vmap stack.

Verify:
local.

